  ├──────────────────┼──────────────┼──────────────┼───────────┤
  │ Acid (0.1N HCl)  │ 24 hours     │ 3.2%          │ PASS      │
  │ Base (0.1N NaOH) │ 24 hours     │ 5.8%          │ PASS      │
  │ Oxidative (3% H₂O₂)│ 24 hours  │ 8.1%          │ PASS      │
  │ Thermal (60°C)   │ 7 days       │ 2.4%          │ PASS      │
  │ Photolytic (ICH) │ 1.2M lux-hr  │ 1.1%          │ PASS      │
